# Dzerzhinskoye, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Dzerzhinskoye () is a rural locality (a selo) in Khasavyurtovsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia.  There are 42 streets.
Geography
Dzerzhinskoye is located 39&nbsp;km north of Khasavyurt (the district's administrative centre) by road. Utsmiyurt is the nearest rural locality.
